func (c *EventConsumer) registerHandlerForTopic(consumer *kafka.Consumer, topic string) {
	switch topic {
	case kafka.TopicUserCreated:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicUserCreated, c.handleUserCreated)
	case kafka.TopicUserUpdated:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicUserUpdated, c.handleUserUpdated)
	case kafka.TopicProfileCreated:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicProfileCreated, c.handleProfileCreated)
	case kafka.TopicProfileUpdated:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicProfileUpdated, c.handleProfileUpdated)
	case kafka.TopicProfileDeleted:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicProfileDeleted, c.handleProfileDeleted)
	case kafka.TopicSwipeCreated:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicSwipeCreated, c.handleSwipeCreated)
	case kafka.TopicMatchCreated:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicMatchCreated, c.handleMatchCreated)
	case kafka.TopicMatchDeleted:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicMatchDeleted, c.handleMatchDeleted)
	case kafka.TopicMediaUploaded:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicMediaUploaded, c.handleMediaUploaded)
	case kafka.TopicMediaDeleted:
		consumer.RegisterHandler(kafka.TopicMediaDeleted, c.handleMediaDeleted)
	}
}
